file.name: bad_format.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers: []
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Pets Store
paths:
  /pets:
    parameters:
      - name: query-param-int32
        in: query
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          uniqueItems: true
          enum:
            - 1
            - 2
            - 7
      - name: query-param-invalid-format
        in: query
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: invalid
          enum:
            - 1
            - 2
            - 7
      - name: query-param-collection-format-and-uniqueItems
        in: query
        explode: true
        schema:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          uniqueItems: true
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Returns all the pets
